data.title: Electric Scooters Australia - Buy E Scooters Online
data.meta_description: Buy electric scooters online Now! Located in Brisbane we carry all the largest stock in Australia. eScooter Servicing also available!
data.text:
Havent set the bike up yet as it is a birthday present for my son however, the whole process of purchase was easy & quick from start to finish. iScoot were very informative about the order, had quick replies to emails and queries and answered all my questions (unlike most companies that just say I dont know). They made the shipping process fast & recieved the item within 14 days of it arriving in their warehouse to WA. Awesome customer service & experience, will be a returning customer for sure 

I recently bought an bike Mamba Venom from Iscoot in Brisbane. I honestly haven't come across service this good for years. Their knowledge of the product was excellent, communication the same and the bike was delivered really quickly in excellent condition even though I live in country South Australia. The tracking system was really good. After my order was dispatched Iscoot rang me to say it was on its way and that I was eligible for a bonus helmet valued at over $100. They didn't have to do this. I felt really comfortable dealing with them throughout the whole process and in these days of internet fraud its hard to be 100% confident that you are dealing with honest companies. Thanks to the staff at Iscoot Brisbane that I dealt with for your excellent service. Lou
